      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 17,
      "referenceLabel": "2 Corinthians 10:17",
      "text": "ܗܘ ܕܝܢ ܕܡܫܬܒܗܪ ܒܡܪܝܐ ܢܫܬܒܗܪ ܀",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "peshitta:second-corinthians.10.18",
      "translationId": "peshitta",
      "bookSlug": "second-corinthians",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 18,
      "referenceLabel": "2 Corinthians 10:18",
      "text": "ܠܐ ܗܘܐ ܓܝܪ ܡܢ ܕܢܦܫܗ ܡܫܒܚ ܗܘ ܗܘ ܒܩܐ ܐܠܐ ܡܢ ܕܡܪܝܐ ܢܫܒܚܝܘܗܝ ܀",
